    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Solo violão: 23 23 23  22 23 22 34 32 34 32 45  44 45 44 42 41 44 34 34 34</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">             54 42 32 32 32    23 25 23 25 23   23 25 23 25 23</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">             32 34 32 34  22 34 44  32 45 42 40</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Intr: A7  D6 B7  Em A7  D6 D/C  G/B Gm6/Bb  D/A D/F#   A7/E A7 D6</span>\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D6\">D6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Aqui có no terreiro</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pelú adié</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A/G\">A/G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Faz inveja pra gente</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D6\">D6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que não tem mulher (bis)</span>\n\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">No jacutá de preto velho</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7/C#\">A7/C#</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D6\">D6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Há uma festa de yaô (bis)</span>\n\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ôi tem nêga de Ogum</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A/G\">A/G</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D6\">D6</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm7\">Bm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">De Oxalá, de Iemanjá</span>\n\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/A\">B/A</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em/G\">Em/G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mucama de Oxossi é caçador</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7/C#\">A7/C#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ora viva Nanã</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">       1º  D6 Bm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nanã buruku (bis)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">       2º  D7/13</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7/6\">G7/6</span> % <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D6\">D6</span> %\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Yô yôo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7/6\">G7/6</span> % <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D6\">D6</span> %\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Yô yôoo</span>\n\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D6/9\">D6/9</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C6/9\">C6/9</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7/9\">B7/9</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">No terreiro de preto velho iaiá</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7/C#\">A7/C#</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7/E\">A7/E</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7/C#\">A7/C#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vamos saravá (a quem meu pai?)</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D9\">D9</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Xangô! (bis)</span>\n",
